  <summary>3/25/1987--Introduced.
Student Loan Bankruptcy Prevention Act - Amends Federal bankruptcy law to exempt student loans made, insured, or guaranteed by a governmental unit from the debts which may be discharged in a chapter 13 (adjustment of debts of individuals with regular income) bankruptcy claim.</summary>
